						<p>Outside of work, I'm a husband, father, dog person, and lifelong Green Bay Packers fan.</p>

						<div class="education-pills-container">
							<div class="education-pill">
								<i class="fa-solid fa-certificate"></i>
								<span class="education-text">
									<strong>Certificate in Full Stack Web Development</strong>
									<span class="education-divider">|</span>
									Northwestern University
								</span>
							</div>
							<div class="education-pill">
								<i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>
								<span class="education-text">
									<strong>MA in Communications</strong>
									<span class="education-divider">|</span>
									Southern New Hampshire University
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

